Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:02.44,Black Signs,Book,0000,0000,0000,,Attendance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.85,0:00:06.15,Main-Tanabe,Танабэ,0000,0000,0000,,Well, summer vacation starts tomorrow,\N but don't go too crazy. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:14.68,Main,Takao,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.35,0:00:17.53,Main,Takao,0000,0000,0000,,let's go to the beach tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:18.95,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:21.77,Main,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,I suddenly have a craving for watermelon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.77,0:00:23.04,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:24.66,Main,Takao,0000,0000,0000,,Let's spit the seeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.66,0:00:25.50,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:59.47,Tandem Riding,Title1,0000,0000,0000,,Tandem\N Riding
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:58.01,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,"Tandem riding."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:07.64,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Summer vacation starts tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:11.31,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the long-awaited\N summer vacation is finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:14.72,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,With no school, I can play as much as I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:16.39,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You better do your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:18.92,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're planning\Nnot to do it tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.92,0:02:21.35,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,because it's only the\Nfirst day of vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:22.66,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.13,0:02:24.44,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:27.37,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,B-But we have to enjoy summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.74,0:02:32.41,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go to the pool and\N the beach, and go camping and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:34.46,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Summer vacation is way too short!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.47,0:02:38.42,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we could have summer vacation forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:39.57,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:42.13,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I like school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.94,0:02:43.89,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:48.66,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,it's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:53.09,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Summer vacation, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:54.98,Main-Nakai,Накай,0000,0000,0000,,So hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:57.21,Main,Mano,0000,0000,0000,,The breeze feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:58.94,Main,Mano,0000,0000,0000,,We need more speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:02.00,Main-Nakai,Накай,0000,0000,0000,,No way, it's way too hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:08.40,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,So hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:16.42,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Should we do what they were doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:17.57,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:19.53,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You go in the front, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:21.77,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,No, we shouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:24.05,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous with the cars and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:27.55,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,There are no cars here,\N and it's not a public road.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.26,0:03:29.27,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:32.06,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Could it be that you're embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:33.73,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:35.94,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you can't do it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:39.57,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? Tandem riding is easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:42.66,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that we shouldn't do it\N because it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:46.52,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the vacant lot, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:47.32,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:55.66,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't do it, you owe me juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:59.84,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just you watch, Такаги-сан.\N Tandem riding is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:05.68,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,That one doesn't count!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:07.14,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:11.31,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Juice it is, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:12.52,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:16.48,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}T-Tandem riding is this hard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:20.34,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Такаги-сан, you're not throwing us\Noff balance on purpose, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:21.84,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:23.00,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:25.41,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just sitting how I usually sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:28.16,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't do it, it's all\N because of you, Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:32.20,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Because when I did this last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:34.11,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,the person in front was able\N to peddle smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:37.43,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really? That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:39.46,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,A girl... friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:42.17,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. Not a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:43.81,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:52.52,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,One more time. I've almost got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:54.07,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:55.52,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get it this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:58.80,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn... I feel frustrated for some reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:04:59.98,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.47,0:05:03.36,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Are you getting aggressive?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:06.70,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not!\N I just don't want to buy you juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:10.07,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, I just don't want to\N buy her a drink. That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:16.91,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we're moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:18.87,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Нисиката,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:21.59,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,the last time I went tandem riding,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:22.92,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,It was with my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.09,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.81,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I think I was four years old at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:35.12,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.28,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:43.65,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.73,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Нисиката, you're not getting a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:49.32,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:52.03,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:55.94,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't tell her I have no money to buy my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:58.96,Grape Cider,Can,0000,0000,0000,,Grape Cider
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:58.96,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:05.38,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,No... thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:09.39,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's gonna say it's an indirect kiss\N or whatever and make fun of me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:12.43,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kid yourself. Have a sip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.06,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't want any.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:17.98,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Endure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:22.00,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need to endure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:28.36,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Here, you're going to get heatstroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.95,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I-I can have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:31.75,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:34.48,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,because...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:39.12,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,you get too embarrassed\Nabout an indirect kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.12,0:06:44.31,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:47.34,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:49.34,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:51.19,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.68,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:01.35,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be walking home\N from school for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:04.70,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah. It's summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:07.48,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:12.20,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from tomorrow, let's practice\N tandem riding here until noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:13.23,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:15.89,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's okay. But not on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:18.41,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we'll just ride here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:22.15,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,If we're only riding here, there's\N no point in practicing, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:24.09,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,No, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:29.72,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Summer vacation starts tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:32.68,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:37.21,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then! Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:42.10,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Summer vacation, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:45.51,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait for summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:48.44,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:52.14,First day,Title2,0000,0000,0000,,First\N Day of\N Summer\N Vacation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:51.30,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,"First Day of Summer Vacation."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:56.00,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0000,0000,0000,,To think it would rain on the first\N day of summer vacation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:08:00.44,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,My summer vacation plans are ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:02.48,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,It's just for a day. Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:04.64,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,I was supposed to go to the pool today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:07.04,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never getting the time back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:08.52,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:12.65,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we can do about the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:14.38,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start our homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:15.59,Main-Mina,Мина&Санаэ,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:17.65,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "Huh?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:19.56,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you didn't bring your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:24.13,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,I told you we should do our homework since\N we can't do anything because of the rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:26.00,Main-Mina,Мина&Санаэ,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I misheard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:27.02,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:30.74,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have homework during\N summer vacation in the first place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:32.51,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:34.47,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have a vacation during vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:35.72,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:37.97,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,But we do have homework,\Nso we have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:53.49,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, jeez! Юкари-тян,\N quit doing your homework and relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:55.33,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,Doing your homework in front of me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:57.72,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,reminds me of homework,\N and I can't enjoy myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:00.10,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,Not my problem! \NYou {\i1}should{\i0} be reminded of homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:03.14,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,It's only the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:05.44,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget about homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:12.66,Italics,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,That's typical of a person who will be\N crying with regret on August 31st.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:14.86,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,You're so stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.57,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just gonna read manga, so there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:18.24,100 % Unrequited,Manga,0000,0000,0000,,100% Unrequited Love
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.08,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:25.10,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,Юкари-тян...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:29.54,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,Can we write our book report on manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:30.93,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:34.06,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,Can you two just go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:39.43,Black Signs,Title3,0000,0000,0000,,Test of Courage
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:38.49,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,"Test of Courage."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:46.45,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Good, it stopped raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:49.90,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why am I happy about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:56.58,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:04.42,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:06.96,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we made a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.26,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:12.59,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:16.30,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, n-no... It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:19.38,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so many puddles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:22.47,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,It really poured last night, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:24.93,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't recognize her for a second there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:29.62,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think of it, I ran into her\N coincidentally a few times on our days off,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:31.83,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but this is our first time meeting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:36.36,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could this be what people call a date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:38.50,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, no! That's not what this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:40.75,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're just practicing tandem riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:42.16,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:44.03,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:46.24,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Were you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:48.63,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:52.59,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,We can't tandem ride in this condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:54.71,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.14,0:10:58.89,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to go out in the\N afternoon right after our practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:03.18,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pain to go back home, so will\N you hang out with me to kill some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:07.22,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-Is this... a date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:09.70,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, no, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:14.82,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so. But someplace\N where there aren't many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:18.23,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no telling what our classmates\Nwould say if any of them saw us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:19.72,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:22.71,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Then... How about...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:27.34,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,A test of courage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:28.69,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect for summer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:31.53,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it usually done at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:34.71,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I heard it's really dark in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:40.63,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, people say there's a presence here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:43.43,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,What presence?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:47.58,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,This tunnel goes straight,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:50.27,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,but a lot of cars crashed into\N the walls for some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:54.12,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,so they had to make a new\N road beside it instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:12:01.99,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since, the bloodthirsty\N ghosts appear every night
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:03.79,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,in search of cars to prey upon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:06.10,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:09.59,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Around here, there's a rumor\N about being spirited away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:13.70,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, people suddenly disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:16.31,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:19.67,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:22.13,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:26.85,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,It's only noon right now.\N There's no way I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:32.28,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's... way darker than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:38.40,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The breeze is making an odd noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:40.86,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:42.82,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,A paper talisman?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:45.71,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,It's to ward off evil spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:49.72,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,That must mean there's something evil here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:54.32,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Нисиката's scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:56.41,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I'm not! That was only—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:12:57.21,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:12:59.09,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,N-Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:05.30,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,What's this steel barrel doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:07.01,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:09.83,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Check what's inside, Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:10.72,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:12.68,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:15.65,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not scared! I'll look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:17.15,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I'll check it out, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:41.33,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea, Такаги-сан—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:45.23,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Такаги-сан? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:49.51,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Такаги-сан? Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.84,0:13:55.30,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Quit messing with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:14:01.69,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Didn't she say something about...\N being spirited away... or something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:05.15,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Такаги-сан! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:06.61,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Такаги-сан!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:18.04,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you screaming? It's just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:19.37,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Такаги-сан?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:22.77,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You were looking for me just now, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:26.55,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is that what it looked like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:30.65,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn you, Такаги-сан.\N This was what you were after.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:32.89,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:35.74,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,There's a hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:38.40,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you peek inside, Нисиката?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:41.99,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As if I'm gonna fall for the same trick again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:43.86,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't mock me, Такаги-сан!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.94,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's stuck! My hand's stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:50.10,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How's my acting ability, Такаги-сан?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:51.57,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now it's your turn to be scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:55.67,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Такаги-сан, it's like something's pulling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.67,0:14:56.56,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Help—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:15:00.06,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Ni-shi-ka-ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:03.13,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Did I scare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.97,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:06.43,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I found it lying on the ground over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.19,0:15:10.98,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad your hand came loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:16.80,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it. You just wait,\N Такаги-сан. I'll get you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:20.55,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You're way too scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:25.40,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,We're back out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.66,0:15:27.87,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... I couldn't retaliate at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,0:15:30.11,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look, Onii-тян.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:33.57,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Another couple is on a date in the tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:35.65,Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Shush/ Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:41.87,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,She called it a "date."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:44.09,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck was she was talking about, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:45.02,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:46.41,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:48.12,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You're blushing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:52.59,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,The test of courage was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:55.30,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:58.26,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost noon. We should head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:15:59.22,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.63,0:16:01.12,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Нисиката?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:02.02,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:06.31,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,We're going in there again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:08.32,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You scared, Нисиката?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:10.56,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:20.12,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I met my quota for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:20.91,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:25.50,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's summer vacation, yet I still have\Nas many push-ups to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:28.79,Independent Research,Title4,0000,0000,0000,,Summer\NScience Project
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:28.38,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,"Summer Science Project."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:32.38,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the consommé flavor is quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:34.72,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying. Your're teary-eyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:38.26,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,No way. Mine's better than\N your kelp flavor, Санаэ-тян.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:40.12,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,They both sound awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:43.14,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many flavors to choose from,\N so why in the world would you choose those?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:45.85,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,Your watermelon flavor is\N playing it too safe, Юкари-тян.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:48.57,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0000,0000,0000,,Take risks in life whilst young, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:51.36,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,Taking risks on popsicle flavors, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:54.32,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, did you two decide on\N subjects for your science projects?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:55.45,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:56.91,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.08,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Мина?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:16:59.78,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still thinking, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:04.04,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there something easy to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:06.06,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,Like, something I can finish in a day?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:07.94,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,You should do actual research.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:11.34,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0000,0000,0000,,How about an observation diary on a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:14.67,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea! That sounds so easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:17.54,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,They basically behave the same every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:20.00,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,so all I have to do is copy and paste\N and change the dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:22.39,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,Write it by hand, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:26.89,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, a dog's day consists\N of waking up, barking for a walk,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:29.27,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,barking to be fed, sleeping,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:33.44,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,barking for attention, and\N barking to be fed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:36.12,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,Why bother doing research about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:38.19,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a stick-in-the-mud, Юкари-тян.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.19,0:17:40.45,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she is the class president, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:42.36,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,She can't help it, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:43.70,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:45.01,Italics,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,Damn these two...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:48.18,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, are you guys doing your homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:52.41,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0000,0000,0000,,There's still time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.81,0:17:54.00,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:57.97,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know,\Nyou're not copying my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:17:59.17,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:01.97,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do your independent\N research for you in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:03.47,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,On a dog, right? No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:07.23,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,You say that now, but you're gonna\N end up sharing your answers with us anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.98,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0000,0000,0000,,She is the class president, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:10.08,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:13.89,Italics,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should do an observation diary on\N these two for my independent research.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:18.40,Tap Water,Title5,0000,0000,0000,,Water Tap
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:16.98,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,"Water Tap."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:21.22,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:25.04,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the worst day of summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.09,0:18:28.00,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:29.62,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I overslept this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:31.37,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:33.97,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then I had a flat tire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:39.18,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's a good thing it happened on\N the day we're not practicing tandem riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:42.31,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Такаги-сан said she's\N going on a family vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:44.69,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was she coming back today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:49.83,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I put off going out during the day\N to help do chores around the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:51.60,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but they still made me go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:54.18,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the worst summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:56.97,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just write that in my one-liner diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:18:58.90,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:02.58,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.11,0:19:05.38,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's Такаги-сан.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:09.83,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's back already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.73,0:19:13.54,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right, I'm gonna follow her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:18.15,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I can find a\N weakness of some sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:36.31,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did she... I think she saw me just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:38.69,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, maybe it's my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:41.58,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She noticed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:44.45,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I can see your hat, Такаги-сан.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:46.91,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're trying to surprise me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:48.47,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Time for a pre-emptive strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:50.50,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna write that in my one-liner diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:20:00.05,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sh-She got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:01.63,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:04.01,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Just grocery shopping...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:07.54,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.96,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go together. Tandem riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:12.69,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, no tandem riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:13.56,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.77,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When did she find out I was following her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:17.73,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's walk together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.53,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Watch out, Такаги-сан!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:24.82,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.81,0:20:27.78,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, today is the worst day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:30.50,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You're hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:33.46,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no. It's nothing. Just leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:36.32,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,No, you should wash it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:46.80,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:48.76,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:50.27,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.51,0:20:53.03,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that I was already having a bad day,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:54.73,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,and now I got injured, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:58.02,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking this is the worst\N summer vacation ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:02.40,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jeez... What should I write\Nfor my diary homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:03.20,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:04.41,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:06.79,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, it's gonna get dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:08.70,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:11.94,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:26.05,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,That feels nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:30.10,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You tried to help me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:30.98,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:32.77,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:37.44,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You should come in, too.\N It's nice and cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:39.86,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:41.59,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Come in already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.69,0:21:46.78,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Cools you down, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:49.01,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:52.15,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I had a good summer vacation day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:55.70,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I got to see a certain somoene today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:21:59.41,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:01.27,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hand you your souvenir tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.39,0:22:06.38,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop that, Такаги-сан, that's cold!
